des:
Super easy skill for new, interesting and super amazing facts and history. Just ask Alexa for Facts of the Day as many times as you want to get new and interesting facts every time.

Just say, Alexa! Fact of the Day OR
Alexa! Open Fact of the Day OR
Alexa! Ask Fact of the Day OR
Alexa! Tell Fact of the Day.
